## Files Changed (implementation-only, per 2b constraints)

1. `promptnotes/src/lib/domain/edit-past-note-start/classify-current-session.ts`
   - Signature widened to 3 params: (state, request, currentNote)
   - Added same-note detection: request.noteId === state.currentNoteId → { kind: 'same-note' }
   - Fixed isEmpty: block-based (single empty paragraph, NoteOps.isEmpty canonical)
   - Old body-string isEmpty removed

2. `promptnotes/src/lib/domain/edit-past-note-start/flush-current-session.ts`
   - Second param changed from selectedNoteId: NoteId | null to request: BlockFocusRequest
   - Added same-note case: returns { result: 'same-note-skipped' } with no I/O
   - SwitchError.pendingNextNoteId → pendingNextFocus: { noteId, blockId }
   - SaveError mapping updated: fs/not-found and fs/unknown now covered explicitly

3. `promptnotes/src/lib/domain/edit-past-note-start/start-new-session.ts`
   - Complete rewrite: PastNoteSelection → BlockFocusRequest + CurrentSessionDecision
   - Same-note path: reuses decision.note, no hydration
   - Cross-note path: hydrates via parseMarkdownToBlocks(snapshot.body)
   - Emits BlockFocused (replaces EditorFocusedOnPastNote)
   - NewSession.focusedBlockId = request.blockId

4. `promptnotes/src/lib/domain/edit-past-note-start/pipeline.ts`
   - Input struct: { request: BlockFocusRequest, currentState, currentNote, previousFrontmatter }
   - Removed SameNoteNoOp type; pipeline always returns Ok(NewSession) on success
   - Added PC-001 check: cross-note + snapshot=null → throw
   - Added PC-004 check: editing/save-failed + currentNote=null → throw
   - Removed pre-pipeline same-note guard (now handled by classifyCurrentSession)
   - hydrateSnapshot port removed; parseMarkdownToBlocks port added

